title: Sunshine On Leith 2013 OST Movie Soundtrack MP3-pong
description:
Sunshine on Leith is a 2013 Scottish musical film directed by Dexter Fletcher. It is an adaptation of the stage musical of the same name, a jukebox musical featuring songs by The Proclaimers.[2] It was screened in the Special Presentation section at the 2013 Toronto International Film Festival.[2][3]

The songs, arranged by musical director Paul Englishby,[4] are performed by the cast. The Proclaimers themselves appear in a brief cameo.[5]
